ences ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[https://www.censusindia.gov.in/2011census/dchb/0303_PART_B_DCHB_JALANDHAR.pdf List of villages in Jalandhar district] at [[Census of India, 2011]]\n\n{{Jalandhar district}}\n<!-- Please Note: Do not add any promotional\n information on this page. Any promotional/spam\n Links or any other information added will be\n removed immediately -->\n\n[[Category:Villages in Jalandhar district]]\n\n\n{{PunjabIN-geo-stub}}\n", "name_user": "SDZeroBot", "label": "safe", "comment": "Stub sorting: replacing PunjabIN-geo-stub with Jalandhar-geo-stub", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lutera_Khurd"}
