ork\">{{cite web|last=Balfour|first=Jay|url=http://pitchfork.com/reviews/albums/21440-cuzznz/|title=Snoop Dogg / Daz Dillinger: Cuzznz|work=Pitchfork Media|accessdate=July 14, 2016}}</ref>\n}}\n'''''Cuzznz''''' is the collaborative [[studio album]] by the American [[West coast hip hop]] recording artists [[Daz Dillinger]] and [[Snoop Dogg]]. It was released on January 15, 2016, by Felder Entertainment Inc.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/cuzznz/id1064207645|title=Cuzznz by Daz & Snoop|publisher=[[iTunes Store]]. [[Apple Inc.|Apple]]|accessdate=December 23, 2015}}</ref> ''Cuzznz'' has [[guest appearance]]s from [[D\u00e2m-Funk|D\u00e2m-funk]], [[Kurupt]] and Shon'Lawon.\n\n== Singles ==\nThe track \"Sho You Right\" was released on [[SoundCloud]] on October 26, 2015.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://soundcloud.com/empire/daz-snoop-bestfriend|title=SHO YOU RIGHT - DAZ N SNOOP FEAT SHON'LA'WON -PRODUCED BY DAM FUNK- FROM THE CUZZNZ ALBUM|publisher=[[SoundCloud]] (US)|accessdate=December 23, 2015}}</ref> The song was produced by [[D\u00e2m-Funk|D\u00e2m-funk]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hotnewhiphop.com/snoop-dogg-and-daz-dillinger-sho-you-right-prod-by-dam-funk-new-song.1966917.html|title=Snoop Dogg & Daz Dillinger drop a super funky track \"Sho You Right.\"|publisher= |website=hotnewhiphop|accessdate=December 23, 2015}}</ref>\n\n\"Best Friend\" was leaked via SoundCloud on December 3, 2015,<ref>{{cite web|url=https://soundcloud.com/empire/daz-snoop-bestfriend|title=Daz & Snoop - Best Friend (Prod. @kjconteh)|publisher= |website=[[SoundCloud]] (US)|accessdate=December 23, 2015}}</ref> and released along with the pre-order of the album on same day. It was officially released as the album's first single. The song was produced by kjconteh.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hotnewhiphop.com/daz-dillinger-and-snoop-dogg-best-friend-new-song.1967534.html|title=Daz & Snoop share another track, \"Best Friend,\" off their upcoming joint album \"Cuzznz.\"|publisher= |website=hotnewhiphop|accessdate=December 23, 2015}}</ref>\n\nOn January 14, 2016, \"N My Life Tyme\" was released.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hotnewhiphop.com/snoop-dogg-and-daz-dillinger-n-my-life-tyme-prod-by-dam-funk-new-song.1968073.html|title=Snoop, Daz, Kurupt & Dam-Funk -- doesn't get much better than that.|publisher= |website=hotnewhiphop}}</ref> The song was produced by D\u00e2m-funk.\n\n==Track listing==\n{{Track listing\n| all_writing = \n| headline = ''Cuzznz''{{nobold|&nbsp;\u2014 North American standard version}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.discogs.com/Daz-N-Snoop-Cuzznz/release/7866666|title=Daz N Snoop - Cuzznz |publisher= |website=[[Discogs]]|accessdate=December 23, 2015}}</ref>\n| extra_column    = Producer(s)\n| title1          = Have U Eva\n| note1           = \n| length1         = 3:50\n| extra1          = [[D\u00e2m-Funk|D\u00e2m-funk]]\n\n| title2          = N My System\n| note2           = featuring [[D\u00e2m-Funk|D\u00e2m-funk]]\n| length2         = 5:19 \t\n| extra2          = [[D\u00e2m-Funk|D\u00e2m-funk]]\n\n| title3          = Six n'da Morning\n| note3           = featuring [[Kurupt]]\n| length3         = 3:09\n| extra3          = [[Jansport J]]\n\n| title4          = Pop Pop Bang\n| note4           = \n| length4         = 3:44\n| extra4          = [[Rick Rock]]\n\n| title5          = Phenomonon\n| note5           = \n| length5         = 3:39\t\n| extra5          =\n\n| title6          = Happy Birthday\n| note6           = \n| length6         = 2:22\t\n| extra6          = [[League Of Starz]]\n\n| title7          = Dic Walk\n| note7           = featuring Kurupt\n| length7         = 4:31\n| extra7          = \n\n| title8          = N My Life Tyme\n| note8           = featuring Kurupt\n| length8         = 4:23\n| extra8          = [[D\u00e2m-Funk|D\u00e2m-funk]]\n\n| title9          = Best Friend\n| note9           = \n| length9         = 4:13\n| extra9          = [[KJ Conteh]]\n\n| title10          = Sho You Right\n| note10      